00:04:10,928 --> 00:04:14,728
- I'm here. What's up? 
 - I had a nightmare

19
00:04:14,728 --> 00:04:18,240
that a monster was coming to eat me.

20
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:23,068
I fought with it all night.

21
00:04:24,388 --> 00:04:27,248
Finally, I drove the monster away.

22
00:04:27,248 --> 00:04:32,168
I didn't have it eat me, and I'm still alive.

23
00:04:34,808 --> 00:04:40,268
It's okay now. I'm here.

24
00:04:55,048 --> 00:05:02,808
Xiao Tuo, what's wrong? What happened?

25
00:05:03,775 --> 00:05:06,009
What's the matter?

26
00:05:06,748 --> 00:05:10,444
Are you sick? You're talking nonsense.

27
00:05:11,588 --> 00:05:16,088
Why is there so much water on the floor? Did you do this?

28
00:05:16,088 --> 00:05:19,148
Xiao Tuo, don't scare me.

29
00:05:19,148 --> 00:05:23,588
I'm a bit tired after fighting the monster all night.

30
00:05:23,588 --> 00:05:26,339
I want to go inside and rest for a while.

31
00:06:22,128 --> 00:06:25,226
This is the prescription I made for you yesterday.

32
00:06:25,948 --> 00:06:31,068
The Riluzole is one of the drugs proven to be effective

33
00:06:31,068 --> 00:06:33,808
in delaying the development of this disease.

34
00:06:33,808 --> 00:06:38,250
Besides this drug, you can also take antioxidants like vitamin E, vitamin C,

35
00:06:38,250 --> 00:06:41,468
and Coenzyme Q10.

36
00:06:42,008 --> 00:06:45,068
What effect does it have?

37
00:06:45,068 --> 00:06:48,848
This drug will not cure the disease,

38
00:06:48,848 --> 00:06:55,508
but it can effectively slow the disease progression.

39
00:06:55,508 --> 00:06:59,748
So this drug is very important to you.

40
00:07:28,908 --> 00:07:34,162
 Xiao Tuo, I don't know what happened to you. 

41
00:07:34,708 --> 00:07:37,536
 Nor do I know how to comfort you. 

42
00:07:38,248 --> 00:07:43,448
 But don't hide anything from me. 

43
00:07:43,448 --> 00:07:49,128
 I will always be here for you and love you, Xiao Que. 

44
00:08:04,220 --> 00:08:09,960
   

45
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:13,698
- Hello, how much is the bill for table five? 
 - Just scan the code and pay.

46
00:08:14,488 --> 00:08:16,743
Please come again.

47
00:08:22,369 --> 00:08:26,309
 Xiao Que, let's break up. 

48
00:08:43,008 --> 00:08:46,708
Lin Tuo, open the door. It's me, open the door.

49
00:08:47,968 --> 00:08:50,668
Lin Tuo, open the door.

50
00:08:50,668 --> 00:08:55,148
Lin Tuo, get the door open. I know you're there. Open the door.

51
00:08:55,148 --> 00:08:58,508
Be gentle. I'll make a call.

52
00:08:59,308 --> 00:09:01,308
Hurry up.

53
00:09:05,420 --> 00:09:07,570
   

54
00:09:13,888 --> 00:09:15,608
Nothing. He's not there.

55
00:09:15,608 --> 00:09:19,968
Okay, I'll call the locksmith now. I have to open this door.

56
00:09:19,968 --> 00:09:22,061
It's illegal. You're not the landlord.

57
00:09:22,061 --> 00:09:25,028
The resident is inside, and you're picking the lock.

58
00:09:25,028 --> 00:09:28,101
What? He's cheating on Que. Why isn't he against the law?

59
00:09:28,101 --> 00:09:32,415
 Cheating isn't against the law, but trespassing is. 

60
00:09:32,415 --> 00:09:35,276
Fine, you're on his side.

61
00:09:35,276 --> 00:09:38,169
- I... 
 - You must know something. Chen Guangpu, tell me what you know.

62
00:09:38,169 --> 00:09:40,928
- Tell me now. 
 - Can you calm down?

63
00:09:40,928 --> 00:09:44,248
Isn't it normal for a couple to have a fight and break up?

64
00:09:44,248 --> 00:09:49,058
What's all the fuss about? Did you see Lin Tuo cheating?

65
00:09:49,058 --> 00:09:50,668
- What did you say? 
 - What are you doing?

66
00:09:50,668 --> 00:09:53,968
- Hitting you is the evidence. Shut up. 
 - Don't hit me.

67
00:09:53,968 --> 00:09:57,148
- Don't hit me. Stop. 
 - Don't lift my leg.

68
00:09:57,148 --> 00:10:00,488
- Let me go. 
 - Calm down.

69
00:10:04,628 --> 00:10:06,632
It's normal for a woman to hit a man.

70
00:10:06,632 --> 00:10:09,158
- Get lost. 
 - W-What?

71
00:10:10,328 --> 00:10:12,128
A floral shirt too?

72
00:10:12,128 --> 00:10:17,388
Sister, watch out for men in floral shirts. They're all no good.

73
00:10:17,388 --> 00:10:19,208
What's wrong?

74
00:10:20,108 --> 00:10:21,848
I'm wearing a plaid shirt.

75
00:10:39,738 --> 00:10:43,588
Chen Guangpu might really not know about this.

76
00:10:43,588 --> 00:10:47,059
I pinched his arm as hard as I could. He's such a coward.

77
00:10:47,059 --> 00:10:49,528
He'll spill the beans if I scare him a bit.

78
00:10:49,528 --> 00:10:53,812
This time, I even ruined a pair of sneakers. H-He kept saying he doesn't know anything.

79
00:10:53,812 --> 00:10:56,328
Why did you scold Chen Guangpu?

80
00:10:56,328 --> 00:10:58,388
This has nothing to do with him.

81
00:10:58,388 --> 00:11:01,840
I can't find Lin Tuo, so I was just anxious.

82
00:11:03,928 --> 00:11:08,008
Maybe you stay at my place for a couple of days. I'll ask Chen Guangpu to leave, so I'll spend more time with you.

83
00:11:08,008 --> 00:11:13,348
No. You go on with your work.

84
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:44,400
Brother An.

85
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:46,100
- Xiao Guo, business seems good. 
 - Yes.

86
00:11:46,100 --> 00:11:48,700
Quite a few people. Go handle your business.

87
00:11:48,700 --> 00:11:50,500
All right.

88
00:12:06,930 --> 00:12:08,620
   

89
00:12:12,700 --> 00:12:14,100
Waiting for me?

90
00:12:14,100 --> 00:12:16,900
- What else? 
 - I'll drink some.

91
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:19,300
No way.

92
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,700
Let's go home.

93
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:25,700
Let me drink some.

94
00:12:26,900 --> 00:12:30,400
Lin Tuo.

95
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,300
I know you are there.

96
00:12:35,100 --> 00:12:40,200
 He Xindi almost tore me apart because you broke up with Xiao Que. 

97
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:45,600
 You didn't tell me anything about it. How can I help you with that? 

98
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:49,000
Fine, if you don't want to tell me, that's okay.

99
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:52,800
You should at least offer Xiao Que an explanation.

100
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:56,500
 Did she do anything wrong, so you wanted to break up with her? 

101
00:12:56,500 --> 00:13:00,700
 You didn't ask to break up in person. That's too much. 

102
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:05,800
 We know Xiao Que well, right? 

103
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:09,100
Has she tried to reach out to you?

104
00:13:09,100 --> 00:13:13,400
 No. She hasn't said anything, and just waited for you to explain everything to her. 

105
00:13:14,300 --> 00:13:18,600
 You understand what I mean, right? 

106
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:22,400
 It's up to you. I'm leaving now. 

107
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:40,890
I'm really leaving.

108
00:13:40,890 --> 00:13:42,900
 Call me. 

109
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:08,500
She was already here when I got here. I wonder if she even left last night.

110
00:14:08,500 --> 00:14:11,800
She did. She had a video call with me when she got home.

111
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:15,300
Can't she just go to his company? Lin Tuo has to go to work.

112
00:14:16,100 --> 00:14:17,900
- Don't mention Lin Tuo. 
 - Okay.

113
00:14:17,900 --> 00:14:20,500
She's still waiting.

114
00:14:20,500 --> 00:14:24,600
Lin Tuo has to come to find her to explain. She told me not to look for Lin Tuo.

115
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:28,600
- She's so upset. 
 - There must be something between them that we don't know about.

116
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:32,900
Of course. So we can only sit and watch her now.

117
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,900
Welcome.

118
00:14:41,300 --> 00:14:43,400
Don't mention Lin Tuo.

119
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:59,100
- Chief Designer. 
 - You...

120
00:15:02,100 --> 00:15:03,400
It's okay.

121
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:05,700
It's not ALS, right?

122
00:15:08,100 --> 00:15:11,600
It's diagnosed as ALS.

123
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:15,300
I mean, I'm fine now.

124
00:15:17,070 --> 00:15:18,700
Let's get to work, Chief Designer.

125
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:21,900
No. You have the day off and I'll go to the hospital with you.

126
00:15:21,900 --> 00:15:25,500
No, it's already been diagnosed.

127
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:27,100
I don't need the day off.

128
00:15:27,100 --> 00:15:30,200
Why are you still going to work? Is working important now?

129
00:15:31,900 --> 00:15:33,730
Chief Designer.

130
00:15:35,190 --> 00:15:38,200
I don't have much time left to work.

131
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:54,200
Lin Tuo, your cafe has launched a new product.

132
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:57,000
Is this Honey Peach Coffee sweet?

133
