138
00:16:13,700 --> 00:16:16,300
Now you have to talk about sales volume, right?

139
00:16:16,300 --> 00:16:19,400
Who's been telling me sales volume are the most important?

140
00:16:19,400 --> 00:16:21,800
What's wrong with you now?

141
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:25,600
Different approaches for different products. Do you have to be that persistent?

142
00:16:25,600 --> 00:16:28,100
Wei Haiyang, are you crazy?

143
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:32,100
You insisted not to let Lin Tuo attend the Young Designers Exhibition before.

144
00:16:32,100 --> 00:16:35,400
And now you insist on putting his work in the prime spot.

145
00:16:35,400 --> 00:16:37,900
Have you lost your mind? What do you want?

146
00:16:37,900 --> 00:16:42,000
I have lost my mind. The dining table must be put in the prime spot.

147
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:44,500
This dining table matters now.

148
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:47,500
It matters to Lin Tuo or the company?

149
00:16:47,500 --> 00:16:49,800
It matters to me!

150
00:16:57,700 --> 00:17:01,000
A'Bao, where are they?

151
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,900
One is inside, and the other goes out.

152
00:17:02,900 --> 00:17:06,900
Okay. If Xiao Que asks about me when she comes back,

153
00:17:06,900 --> 00:17:10,200
just tell her that I have already been here, okay?

154
00:17:11,300 --> 00:17:13,000
I'm leaving.

155
00:17:13,700 --> 00:17:16,300
Chen Guangpu, come back here!

156
00:17:16,300 --> 00:17:19,600
Can you... Can you let me go?

157
00:17:19,600 --> 00:17:21,000
- Why are you running? 
 - Wait.

158
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:24,700
Can't you have them solve the problem between the two of them? Don't come to me.

159
00:17:24,700 --> 00:17:27,400
- Did you see him or not? Tell me. 
 - I didn't see him.

160
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:30,800
We are not like you. If my buddy has a problem, he solves it himself.

161
00:17:30,800 --> 00:17:33,400
It's not like you who have to team up and fight.

162
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:35,400
- You two went to the restroom together. 
 - We are all adults.

163
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:38,000
- You must've seen him. You've seen him, right? 
 - Let's keep some distance.

164
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:40,200
- We are different. 
 - Are you lying to me? You've seen him.

165
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:42,400
We don't talk about everything. It's his own business...

166
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:44,700
- Chen Guangpu. 
 - Xiao Que.

167
00:17:44,700 --> 00:17:47,000
Wait here.

168
00:17:58,700 --> 00:18:00,800
Here are the earphones for him.

169
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:04,400
And some bread for breakfast.

170
