197
00:20:21,300 --> 00:20:24,400
 I just saw Que. She said she'll wait for you at HW Cafe tonight. 

198
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:29,000
 No matter what, go and make yourself clear. Don't be ambiguous, as it's really not necessary. 

