211
00:21:22,700 --> 00:21:24,400
I see.

212
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:28,500
- Then, go do your thing. 
 - Okay.

213
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:30,500
I have prepared the meals for you.

214
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:33,700
- You can order anything you want to eat. 
 - Okay.

215
00:21:33,700 --> 00:21:36,900
I'm leaving now, bye.

216
00:21:56,100 --> 00:21:59,100
A'Bao, you don't need to work overtime today.

217
00:21:59,100 --> 00:22:00,900
Just put them there. I'll wash.

