Why did you come back?

257
00:26:11,500 --> 00:26:14,600
- Xiao Ye. 
 - Xiao Ye isn't home.

258
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:18,400
Where has he gone this late?

259
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:21,870
Mom, don't call him yet.

260
00:26:21,870 --> 00:26:24,200
I have something to tell you and dad.

261
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:29,000
Something important.

262
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:33,800
What is it?

263
00:26:34,900 --> 00:26:37,900
Xiao Ye has got his admission letter...

264
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:41,200
from the Art Academy.

265
00:26:56,600 --> 00:27:00,300
You are so anxious.

266
00:27:00,300 --> 00:27:01,900
Have some fruit.

267
00:27:01,900 --> 00:27:04,200
Why hasn't my brother texted back?

268
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:07,100
- I'll go home. 
 - Sit down.

269
00:27:09,600 --> 00:27:12,100
Stay here and wait.

270
00:27:13,500 --> 00:27:17,400
You're only going to make things worse by going back.

271
00:27:18,200 --> 00:27:21,600
- Can my brother convince my dad? 
 - Definitely not.

272
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:24,800
No one can't convince your dad.

273
00:27:24,800 --> 00:27:28,100
Then what's the point of me waiting here?

274
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:33,700
Just stay here. Your brother knows what he's doing.

275
00:27:38,300 --> 00:27:40,600
What are you doing?

276
00:27:42,100 --> 00:27:44,700
You guys are so thoughtless.

277
00:27:45,400 --> 00:27:48,700
Why hide such a significant matter from us?

278
00:27:49,300 --> 00:27:52,700
- Where is he? Tell him to get back here. 
 - Dad!

279
00:27:52,700 --> 00:27:54,300
Can you listen to me?

280
00:27:54,300 --> 00:27:56,300
What do you want to say?

281
00:27:56,300 --> 00:27:58,600
Do you expect us to accept it?

282
00:27:58,600 --> 00:28:00,700
In your dreams!

283
00:28:00,700 --> 00:28:02,800
You two are so bold.

284
00:28:02,800 --> 00:28:06,100
Your mom and I have worked so hard to cultivate you two.

285
00:28:06,100 --> 00:28:10,000
You didn't listen to us, and even colluded with Xiao Ye.

286
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:14,750
- You just made your decision on such a big matter? How dare you! 
 - Dad!

287
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:18,900
Have you really worked hard to cultivate us?

288
00:28:18,900 --> 00:28:23,000
Did you really do what's best for us all these years?

289
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:26,300
Have you ever cooked for us or washed our clothes?

290
00:28:26,300 --> 00:28:28,700
Have you ever chatted with us?

291
00:28:29,500 --> 00:28:33,400
Do you know what we like? Do you know what we're allergic to?

292
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:36,300
Do you know when we get sick?

293
00:28:36,300 --> 00:28:38,900
You don't know anything.

294
00:28:38,900 --> 00:28:42,300
You're a doctor, yet you don't even know both of us are sick.

295
00:28:42,300 --> 00:28:44,200
You don't know that Xiao Ye has depression.

296
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:47,900
He's only 18 and he doesn't want to live anymore. He wanted to jump off a building. Do you know it?

297
00:28:47,900 --> 00:28:49,700
What?

298
00:28:49,700 --> 00:28:51,700
Xiao Tuo.

299
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:57,100
You're busy with everything at the hospital.

300
00:28:57,100 --> 00:29:00,900
You like the hospital, your career, and being a director.

301
00:29:00,900 --> 00:29:05,300
So you want all of us to work in the hospital, where you like.

302
00:29:05,300 --> 00:29:08,700
Dad, have you ever loved Mom?

303
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:12,300
Have you ever loved us?

304
00:29:16,600 --> 00:29:18,360
Mom...

305
00:29:19,020 --> 00:29:21,300
Have you ever loved us?

306
00:29:26,100 --> 00:29:28,800
- I don't allow you to talk to us like this. 
 - Don't.  
 - Come on.

307
00:29:28,800 --> 00:29:32,800
- Don't. 
 - Hit me! If hitting me...

308
00:29:33,300 --> 00:29:37,800
would make you agree Xiao Ye to attend the art academy, then I'll stand right here and let you hit me

309
00:29:37,800 --> 00:29:40,200
until you are satisfied.

310
00:29:40,900 --> 00:29:44,900
Xiao Ye won't go to medical school, or retake the exam.

311
00:29:44,900 --> 00:29:47,600
He must go to the art academy.

312
00:29:51,100 --> 00:29:53,700
I won't have my little brother jump off a building.

313
00:29:53,700 --> 00:29:56,200
I want him to live well.

314
00:29:57,100 --> 00:30:01,600
To live the life he wants.

315
00:30:11,400 --> 00:30:16,800
Fine. Your sons have grown up, and are truly beyond control now.

316
00:30:17,800 --> 00:30:20,200
You've got the nerve. Just leave.

317
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:23,900
Both of you leave. I don't need sons like you.

318
00:30:42,800 --> 00:30:44,600
Xiao Tuo.

319
00:31:17,500 --> 00:31:21,300
It's okay. Don't worry.

320
00:31:29,300 --> 00:31:33,700
Just stay at my place. I can take care of both of you.

321
00:32:13,500 --> 00:32:15,200
Is Grandpa asleep?

322
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,800
Yes.

323
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:23,200
Xiao Ye.

324
00:32:24,100 --> 00:32:26,400
You stay at Grandpa's place.

325
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:30,500
Dad won't calm down that soon.

326
00:32:30,500 --> 00:32:36,900
When I went to college, he was silent towards me for a year.

327
00:32:37,500 --> 00:32:40,000
No one can handle his temper.

328
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:41,800
I know it.

329
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:46,900
But you have to apologize to Mom.

330
00:32:46,900 --> 00:32:51,200
It hasn't been easy for her to raise you all these years.

331
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:55,900
We can run away from home, but she can't.

332
00:32:55,900 --> 00:32:59,600
Dad will take all his anger out on her alone.

333
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:05,600
She's the one who's hurting the most.

334
00:33:05,600 --> 00:33:09,100
She loves you the most, and you know that.

335
00:33:14,300 --> 00:33:17,700
Stay with Grandpa until school starts.

336
00:33:18,900 --> 00:33:21,400
The school is not far from downtown Chongqing.

337
00:33:21,400 --> 00:33:23,400
Xiao Que and I went to see it specially.

338
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:28,200
It's nice and there's a couple of snack streets around.

339
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:30,600
You two have seen it?

340
00:33:30,600 --> 00:33:33,100
Xiao Que insisted.

341
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:37,700
She said you'd definitely get in.

342
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:42,500
Is she doing well?

343
00:33:44,800 --> 00:33:46,500
Yes.

344
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:54,800
Even if we break up one day,

345
00:33:54,800 --> 00:33:59,200
you can still go to see her. She always thinks about you.

346
00:33:59,200 --> 00:34:01,800
Why would you two break up?

347
00:34:04,600 --> 00:34:07,100
Just saying that.

348
00:34:09,300 --> 00:34:13,800
I'll take care of your tuition and living expenses.

349
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:17,100
Grandpa gave me some, and I've saved some.

350
00:34:17,100 --> 00:34:20,300
I have spent some on a health check-up recently.

351
00:34:20,300 --> 00:34:24,700
If it's not enough, I could figure it out.

352
00:34:24,700 --> 00:34:28,300
What's wrong with you? Why did you get a health check-up?

353
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:32,900
Just a regular check-up. A bit expensive.

354
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:38,700
Then when school starts, I'll come to you.

355
00:34:42,500 --> 00:34:44,600
We'll see then.

356
00:34:44,600 --> 00:34:49,600
Let me know in advance. I might be on a business trip.

357
00:34:55,500 --> 00:34:59,200
All right, go to sleep. I have to get up early tomorrow morning.

358
00:34:59,200 --> 00:35:01,700
I have to go back to work.

359
00:35:01,700 --> 00:35:03,340
Brother.

360
00:35:04,380 --> 00:35:06,200
Thank you.

361
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:11,000
Go to sleep.

362
00:35:14,100 --> 00:35:16,800
   

363
00:35:26,210 --> 00:35:28,385
Where's Lin Tuo?

364
00:35:29,100 --> 00:35:31,500
Why is Lin Tuo taking leave again?

365
00:35:31,500 --> 00:35:34,000
He has always taken leave recently.

366
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:37,500
Unlike us, his girlfriend runs a cafe.

367
