00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:32,800
How dare you hand me a proposal like this!

378
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:36,200
Redo it!

379
00:36:41,100 --> 00:36:43,900
Before Lin Tuo gets sick, he'll get sick first.

380
