00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:26,700
- I should have told you face to face. 
 - Face to face?

404
00:39:34,500 --> 00:39:36,700
Why do you want to break up?

405
00:39:39,500 --> 00:39:41,300
Nothing special.

406
00:39:44,400 --> 00:39:48,600
Lin Tuo, did something happen to you?

407
00:39:48,600 --> 00:39:50,200
No.

408
00:39:51,100 --> 00:39:55,200
Do you think I don't know you after all the time we've been together?

409
00:39:55,200 --> 00:39:59,100
You've seemed distant lately.

410
00:39:59,100 --> 00:40:03,700
You got injured in the face, and you came here to break up with me.

411
